            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Transactis ergo non paucis diebus, supradictus <persName key="#Muslims" ref="#people/1926"
                        >Maio</persName> cum aliquantis <rs key="#Monks">fratribus</rs>, qui a facie
                        <rs key="#Muslims">Agarenorum</rs> fugerant, veniens <placeName ref="#places/173"
                            >Capuam</placeName> [â€¦] Simili quoque modo in <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >episcopio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Bishops" ref="#juridical_persons/1993">Neapolitano</orgName>
                        dederunt <rs key="#Gualdi">gualdum</rs>, quod habebant in <placeName
                            key="#Gualdi" ref="#places/605">Liburias</placeName>, loco ubi dicitur
                        <placeName ref="#places/2805" key="#Gualdi">Cree</placeName> pro quo acceperunt libras
                        argenti centum, eo tenore, ut, quocumque tempore illud recolligere vellent,
                        redderent illis predictas libras argenti, et sua cum pace reciperent.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
