            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The <foreign>Chronicon Vulturnense</foreign> mentions the sale made by Abbot Maio
                    of San Vincenzo to the episcopate of Naples of a <foreign>gualdo</foreign>
                    located in the locus Pantano, in Liburia.</p>
            </div>
